{"tid":2515752,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"古天樂《真·三國無雙》演呂布竟找黑人替身？監製親自說明","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:13:51.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"27d5caeaaeedf16703a13a831831900a9660c764","tid":2515752,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"港星古天樂當年以改編漫畫的穿越劇《尋秦記》爆紅，帥氣古裝扮相令人印象深刻，近日在主演電玩改編的電影《真&middot;三國無雙》飾演「天下第一無雙神兵」的呂布，該片斥資三億，由香港電影金像獎導演周顯揚執導監製，沒想到在網路流傳著一組拍攝花絮照，被曝光劇組為古天樂找來的替身居然是一名黑人，引發大批網友熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbZjuUTeUPE4updaYcP6S3iVst645B6jhu9A52WQkj6D4?filename=YhK1iGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhK1iGh.jpg&h=b409f46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼古天樂在新片《真&middot;三國無雙》中飾演呂布。（圖／双喜電影提供）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTrKQ65s5siVP3dvtVhAEfJQCf7yCMGdeg7PuTPRw9mcL?filename=pMihBs0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMihBs0.jpg&h=cc30ac5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古天樂先前曾在宣傳活動中爆料，他在拍攝《真&middot;三國無雙》時因為手上的兵器太重，被兵器「方天畫戟」尖端撞傷眼球，緊急縫了八針，不過仍堅持拍戲，敬業的精神受到影迷欽佩，近日微博則流傳一組他的替身演員的照片，穿著與他相同的戰袍站在樹林中，仔細一看才發現是位黑人演員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbvEyfBicEFexynr3CcdL1EAa6M7SPnZAUaEZFJRHq3Fs?filename=y3U40UL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy3U40UL.jpg&h=b95b3d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼古天樂在《真&middot;三國無雙》竟找了黑人擔任替身。（圖／翻攝自娛樂眼微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZpFekJj4mbkYAwraymfLys31VN2EcMU8yPayytjTdMgY?filename=SHBZPN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSHBZPN7.jpg&h=8f5fb02e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息一出後《真&middot;三國無雙》的監製杜致朗火速回應，他坦言劇組找黑人演員擔任古天樂替身，並解釋說當時在紐西蘭拍攝，為了凸顯角色呂布的高大與符合古天樂身高，因此找了一位黑人演員，她也透露對方主要是擔任光替與背景替，尤其光替主要幫演員走位、佔位置，並不會出現於正片中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd3dRLWkEYGwZYY2rBy4mhjQqcPZncJSRC1J6VGwrgRpm?filename=ydTxqmw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FydTxqmw.jpg&h=b6638a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲古天樂新片用「黑人替身」監製杜致朗親自回應。（圖／翻攝自杜致朗微博）"},{"pid":"836e4678564b2fa30e8eac5237d577ba954c05bc","tid":2515752,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5606722cede86a7293e22402774eb73cd5a4bbd5","tid":2515752,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fde96c71a7f5e2520165c34b68272be591a421","tid":2515752,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"似就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eacf14efcc303e9330c7571312cfe965f649a8d","tid":2515752,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:13:51.000Z","msg":"BLM ☑️"}]}